## Description

[Nest](https://github.com/nestjs/nest) framework TypeScript starter repository.

## Installation

```bash
$ npm install
```

## Running the app

```bash
# development
$ npm run start

# run client backend watch mode
$ npm run dev:backend

# run grpc service watch mode
$ npm run dev:db

# production mode
$ npm run start:prod
```
